reviewText:
Do not play this game! Even if you got it for free, it is such a waste of time. To make this review short I will list the things I like about this game;

......hmm...Ummm... the bullet drop and target leading was well done, being able to see where your shot landed and compensating with the markers on the scope..

and everything else about it sucks.

